  "spans": [
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0002",
      "text": " 34",
      "bbox": [
        521.04,
        723.59,
        534.92,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0003",
      "text": "4.2.10.3  Request Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        57.65,
        227.06,
        68.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0004",
      "text": "Addressing: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        81.65,
        157.1,
        92.76
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0005",
      "text": "The S_ID field designates the source Nx_Port requesting the LESB.  The D_ID field",
      "bbox": [
        157.08,
        81.65,
        539.99,
        92.76
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0006",
      "text": "shall be set as follows:",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        93.65,
        195.91,
        104.76
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0007",
      "text": "a) to any Domain Controller well known address (FFFCxxh);",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        118.97,
        376.17,
        130.08
      ],
      "block_index": 5,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0008",
      "text": "b) to the F_Port well known address (FFFFEh); or",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        142.96,
        330.7,
        154.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0009",
      "text": "c)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        166.96,
        114.35,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0010",
      "text": "to any Nx_Port logged in with the S_ID address.",
      "bbox": [
        122.37,
        166.96,
        335.15,
        178.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0011",
      "text": "Payload: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        190.96,
        140.41,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0012",
      "text": "The format of the Payload is shown in table 17.",
      "bbox": [
        140.4,
        190.96,
        348.7,
        202.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0013",
      "text": "The requested LESB is identified as follows:",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        310.96,
        290.96,
        322.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0014",
      "text": "a) If the D_ID is a Domain Controller well known address (FFFCxxh), the N_Port_ID field shall be",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        334.96,
        539.98,
        346.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0015",
      "text": "set to an N_Port_ID withihn the associated domain. The LESB requested is for the F_Port that",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        346.96,
        540.06,
        358.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0016",
      "text": "the N_Port_ID is logged in with;",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        358.96,
        262.36,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0017",
      "text": "b) if the D_ID is the F_Port well known address (FFFFFEh), the N_Port_ID field is not meaningful",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        382.96,
        540.14,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0018",
      "text": "and the LESB request is for the local Fx_Port that the S_ID is logged in with; or",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        394.96,
        471.83,
        406.08
      ],
      "block_index": 11,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0019",
      "text": "c)",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        418.96,
        114.33,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0020",
      "text": "for all other D_IDs, the N_Port_ID field is not meaningful and the LESB requested is for the",
      "bbox": [
        122.35,
        418.96,
        539.99,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0021",
      "text": "Nx_Port assigned to the D_ID.",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        430.96,
        257.43,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0022",
      "text": "4.2.10.4  Reply Sequence",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        214.86,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 13,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0023",
      "text": "LS_RJT: ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        478.96,
        138.19,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0024",
      "text": "LS_RJT signifies rejection of the RLS command. The LS_RJT reason code and reason",
      "bbox": [
        138.18,
        478.96,
        539.97,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 2
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0025",
      "text": "code explanation are set as follows:",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        490.96,
        254.26,
        502.08
      ],
      "block_index": 14,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0026",
      "text": "a) If an FC_Port does not support the LESB, it shall reply with an LS_RJT specifying a reason",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        514.96,
        539.96,
        526.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0027",
      "text": "code of \"Unable to perform command request\" (09h) and should respond with a reason code",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        526.96,
        540.06,
        538.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0028",
      "text": "explanation of \"Request not supported\" (2Ch); or",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        538.96,
        337.78,
        550.08
      ],
      "block_index": 15,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0029",
      "text": "b) if the N_Port_ID is not logged in with an F_Port within the domain, the Domain Controller",
      "bbox": [
        106.02,
        562.96,
        540.02,
        574.08
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0030",
      "text": "should reply with an LS_RJT specifying a reason code of \"Logical error\" (03h) and reason code",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        574.96,
        539.87,
        586.08
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p053_s0031",
      "text": "explanation \"Invalid N_Port_ID\" (1Fh).",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        586.96,
        291.11,
        598.08
      ],
      "block_index": 16,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
